    MultipartPathOverlay.ColorPart(
        Color.GREEN,
        Color.WHITE, 
        Color.DKGRAY, 
        Color.LTGRAY
    )
)

multipartPath.map = naverMap







The following code example removes a multipart path overlay from the map.


